Part A: Fractions on the Number Line

Plot 2/3 on a number line divided into thirds.

Plot 5/4 on a number line and label the whole number it passes.

Which is closer to 1?
4/5 or 3/4?

Part B: Equivalent & Simplifying Fractions

Simplify:
a. 12/18
b. 15/25
c. 8/32

Fill in the blank:
___ / 12 = 2/3

Write three fractions equivalent to 1/4.

