Part E: Word Problems

You have 2 pizzas. You give away 3/4 of one pizza and 1/2 of the other.
How much pizza did you give away total?

A garden is 3/5 of an acre. You plant vegetables in 2/3 of the garden.
How many acres are planted?

A ribbon is 5 feet long. You cut off 1/3 ft pieces.
How many pieces can you make?

Part F: Challenge Problems

Which is larger:
7/8 or 13/16?
Explain using a method of your choice.

Fill in the missing numerator:
___ / 15 = 4/5